name: Dashbook
tag_list: mobile, dashboard, real-time, realtime, information, personal-dashboard
overview:
Dashbook is the customizable mobile dashboard that houses everything you, as a developer, care about most. (think services like NewRelic, AWS, GitHub; the news and people that influences you most, and all your important metrics).

Dashbook organizes all of your information in a series of “dashes”. Each dash is a gateway in to a piece of real-time information tailored specifically to you.

You can customize your personal Dashbook by leveraging our Dash Library to add and remove the dashes you need most.

We also built Dashbook with an open specification that allows developers to build their own custom dashes using a few lines of JSON. These dashes can then be uploaded to our dash library and shared with the Dashbook community!
